com.yahoo.bullet.storm.drpc

Class DRPCQueryResultPubscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.bullet.storm.drpc.DRPCQueryResultPubscriber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.yahoo.bullet.pubsub.Publisher, com.yahoo.bullet.pubsub.Subscriber, AutoCloseable

    public class DRPCQueryResultPubscriber
extends Object
implements com.yahoo.bullet.pubsub.Publisher, com.yahoo.bullet.pubsub.Subscriber
    This class is both a query Publisher and a result Subscriber. It uses HTTP to do a request- response call where the request is the Bullet query and the response is the result from the backend.

    • Constructor Detail

      • DRPCQueryResultPubscriber

        public DRPCQueryResultPubscriber(com.yahoo.bullet.common.BulletConfig config)
        Create an instance from a given BulletConfig. Requires DRPCConfig.DRPC_HTTP_CONNECT_TIMEOUT, DRPCConfig.DRPC_HTTP_CONNECT_RETRY_LIMIT, DRPCConfig.DRPC_SERVERS, DRPCConfig.DRPC_HTTP_PORT, and DRPCConfig.DRPC_HTTP_PATH to be set. To be used in PubSub.Context#QUERY_SUBMISSION mode.
        Parameters:
        config - A non-null config that contains the required settings.
